      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enable_comments" data-step-uuid="1A2F2C92-30FB-4A19-A7CA-9253651916D1">
    <h2 id="enable_comments" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enable Comments</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/044/original/38790613-c365-4f27-be33-712be95191db.png" srcset="" alt="Enable Comments" height="78" width="241">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_AD3F3410-215E-0135-A80E-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Allow Comments on this Page</strong> checkbox. You can also make comments public by clicking the <strong>Make Comments Public</strong> checkbox.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

