      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_comment" data-step-uuid="30F52B55-E826-4A8C-9C8E-E3CD54592E98">
    <h2 id="add_comment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Comment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/046/original/bdaa65e4-c96a-49bd-aea6-e1d570be6786.png" srcset="" alt="Add Comment" height="237" width="480">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_AD3FA320-215E-0135-A812-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Below the content of the page, there is a place for comments. You can add a comment by typing in the text box [1] and clicking the <strong>Add Comment</strong> button [2].</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: Users must be logged in to the same Canvas account to make comments regardless of your ePortfolio visibility setting.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_comment" data-step-uuid="1D3F9DE5-3332-4BE5-8728-0233C751E2AF">
    <h2 id="view_comment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Comment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/048/original/614ca624-674f-4092-93ea-a8e7751a0d5b.png" srcset="" alt="View Comment" height="207" width="655">
